    #info
        .content.en
            p(style='white-space:pre;')
                | ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
                | | Eina 50 Anys                                                       |
                | └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
            p
                | This is an interactive logo to commemorate the 50th Anniversary of Eina's Design Foundation in Barcelona:
            p
                | 1. Every day at 00h 00m 00s a new logo will be generated consisting in a set of blocks assorted randomly. 
                | Each block will contain a texture taht may ( or may not ) be animated.
            p
                | 2. Anytime during the day anyone can visit the interactive version of the logo ( currently located at http://proper-code.com/50anys ) 
                | and modify the logo's composition. Either changing the textures in each block ( by clicking on them ) or by deciding if this textures 
                | must be animated or not ( by long clicking on the blocks ).
            p
                | 3. Every day, at 23h 59m 59s, the logo will be saved and a new one will be generated.
            p
                | 4. Previously generated logos will be stored and availabe online in order to be able to see their evolution.
                | They can be visited by clicking prev and next ( or swiping on a mobile ).
            p
                | 5. Each logo version can be exported for print clicking the top-right button ( desktop only )

            p(style='white-space:pre;')
                | The goals of this experience are:
                |   1. Make design a col.laborative experience at everyone's reach
                |   2. Create an evolutionary logo that expresses and shows how time passes
                |   3. Commemorate Eina's 50 year anniversary emphasizing it's diversity and plurality.

